    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;


&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Meaning of Namaste 
    &lt;div id=&#34;meaning-of-namaste&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
